|GKO================================================================
                   |WKOGarou Guild : Howls
|GKO================================================================

|YKOHowl allows the wolf to communicate particular emotions to other
players around Darkwind. This is the primary means of communication
in wolf form. It is also possible to howl to all Garou, by leaving
off the intended target. Current howls include:

|WKBAppreciation   Anger          Agreement      Admiration
Bloodlust      Beckoning      Confusion      Danger
Distress       Disagreement   Farewell       Fear
Fondness       Fatigue        Frustration    Greed
Greetings      Happiness      Home           Hunger
Joy            Lust           Loneliness     Loathing
Laaggg         Laughter       Moonlust       Patience
Passion        Revenge        Reluctance     Suspicion
Sorrow         Sickness       Success        Sadness
Surprise       Suffering      Triumph        Understanding
Warning        Weakness       

|RKOSyntax: |YKBhowl <type> [to <target>]      |WKOCost: |CKO5 sp
